fields.name: .orders <item_name>
fields.value:
Retrieve top 5 sell orders for an item from warframe.market
Usage example:
.orders frost_prime_blueprint

fields.name: .relics <prime_item>
fields.value:
Retrieve relics for a prime item
Usage example:
.relics frost_prime_blueprint

fields.name: .auctions <kuva_weapon>
fields.value:
Retrieve auctions for a kuva weapon lich from warframe.market, sorted by buyout price and weapon damage
Usage example:
.auctions kuva_kohm
